USER:

name
surname
password
email

has_many posts
has_many comments
has_many likes
has_many friend_request
has_many friends through friend_request


---


POST:

title
body
date

has_many likes
has_many comments
belongs_to author (user)


---


COMMENT:

body
date

belongs_to author (user)


---


LIKES:

belongs_to liker (user)
belongs_to liked (post)


---


FRIEND_REQUEST:

status [pending / accepted]

belongs_to sender (user)
belongs_to reciever (user)



